<% content_for :title, "FAQ | Zoomora" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Answers to common questions about ordering, delivery, warranty, and returns at Zoomora." %>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-[15px] py-8 lg:py-14">
  <%= render Ui::BreadcrumbComponent.new(items: [
    { label: "Home", url: root_path },
    { label: "FAQ" }
  ]) %>

  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-[12px] uppercase font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] text-red-600">Need Help?</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-[32px] lg:text-[40px] font-display font-bold text-ink-950 leading-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-body-lg text-grey-500 max-w-xl mx-auto">Answers to what we're asked most. Can't find yours? <%= link_to "Contact us", contact_path, class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium" %> directly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "How long does delivery take?", open: true) do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Delivery is free across the UAE and takes 3–5 working days from order confirmation. Our team also handles professional assembly on delivery at no extra cost, so your ride-on, e-bike, or trampoline is ready to use the moment it arrives.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "Is assembly really included?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Yes — every order includes professional assembly by our delivery team, at no extra charge. If you assemble a product yourself instead, please note that self-assembly voids the manufacturer warranty on that unit.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "What's covered under warranty?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Every powered product — ride-ons, e-bikes, ATVs, dirt bikes, scooters, and golf carts — carries a 12-month manufacturer warranty covering the motor, battery, and electronics against defects. It doesn't cover normal wear (tyres, brake pads) or damage from misuse. See our <%= link_to "Terms & Conditions", terms_and_conditions_path, class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium" %> for full warranty terms.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "Can I return a product if it doesn't work out?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Yes — unused, undamaged items in their original packaging can be returned or exchanged within 7 days of delivery. Once a product has been assembled or used, we can only accept returns for items that arrived damaged or incorrect. Full details are in our <%= link_to "Shipping & Return Policy", shipping_and_returns_path, class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium" %>.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "What age is each product suitable for?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Age and weight guidance is listed on every product page under the Features accordion. As a rough guide: ride-ons suit toddlers and young kids, kick scooters and bicycles suit most ages with the right size, and ATVs, dirt bikes, and golf carts are built for teens and adults, with youth models offering adjustable speed limiters.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "What payment methods do you accept?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>We accept Visa and Mastercard debit and credit cards in AED. Buy Now, Pay Later options are also available at checkout for eligible orders.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "Do I need an account to order?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>You're welcome to browse and check out as a guest. Creating a free account lets you track orders, save items to your wishlist, and check out faster next time — you can <%= link_to "create one here", new_user_registration_path, class: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium" %> in under a minute.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <%= render Ui::AccordionItemComponent.new(title: "Can I cancel or change my order?") do |item| %>
      <% item.with_body do %>
        <p>Orders can be cancelled free of charge within 24 hours of placing them — just contact our team. Once an order has been processed for shipping, it can't be cancelled, but you're welcome to request a return once it arrives.</p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-14 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <%= render Marketing::CtaBannerComponent.new(
      title: "Still Have Questions?",
      description: "Our team is happy to help with anything product-specific or order-related.",
      cta_label: "Contact Us",
      cta_url: contact_path,
      tone: :dark
    ) %>
  </div>
</div>
